name: MOLLYWATR
description:
MOLLYWATR was created exclusively to satisfy the hydration needs of EDM fans in clubs, concerts and festivals world wide. It's ultra crisp uncut natural spring water with natural electrolytes that’s been ozonated to ensure that you get exactly what you’re looking for: a great tasting nonsense free drink to quench your thirst while you get down. Be sure to supercharge this bottle underneath a UV light source to enhance your visual experience. 

MOLLYWATR keeps the party going. 

Let's get hydrated.

Each pallet of MOLLYWATR contains 72 cases. Each case contains 24 16.9 fluid ounce bottles of MOLLYWATR  for your event or establishment.

Free Delivery in the USA!

Allow 10 business days for delivery.
